{"tid":1521752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣國立東華大學校長趙涵㨗　願親往香港保釋 829深水埗警署暴動罪僑生","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T20:36:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":174,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f68b30bb52890c606305751202fac83b5a60e1","tid":1521752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"國立東華大學一名李姓香港女僑生，傳出因涉及8月29日九龍深水埗警署的示威抗議，在香港被捕並被控暴動罪。校方今接獲消息，立即請教育部駐香港代表就近表達關切，校長趙涵㨗說，若需要他願到香港作保，盼李生能早日平安回台上課。<br />\n<br />\n東華大學這學期港生約104人，校方今天接獲同樣在東華就讀的李生友人電郵，得知她被捕訊息，立即了解其他在校港生狀況，目前了解未傳出有其他人有同樣狀況。<br />\n<br />\n根據港媒報導，29日晚間在香港九龍深水埗警署，有示威者集結圍堵警署，並涉嫌以雷射筆照射警署內警員，之後警方執行驅散行動並拘捕18人，其中包括李姓僑生在內的3人，被控暴動罪，3人目前留院接受治療，將於9月3日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n東華大學表示，除了請教育部駐香港代表就近關切，李姓僑生也已請律師處理。學校將進一步關切，會依據相關規定提供李姓僑生最大的關切，學校下周就要開學，希望李姓僑生能儘早獲釋，返校就讀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4021325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F4021325&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=566f6246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4021325</a>"},{"pid":"c1145e8a3e43bda9678287827caab1f861c90869","tid":1521752,"uid":173207,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"呢位校長好愛學生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaac02b9f70f202956aae4a8ad32b374ed2d38d","tid":1521752,"uid":240362,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"香港大學校長同台灣大學校長嘅分別"},{"pid":"f1c40708e539a53ececcdee6bc86d0e12c0162e8","tid":1521752,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57bad80bc69cdd9591c91a2dea8736b44c5d7a2","tid":1521752,"uid":103325,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"校長好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過做擔保要香港人要做得"},{"pid":"45af4252be17f4395b2a46f6410d60a0c164e360","tid":1521752,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e57bad80bc69cdd9591c91a2dea8736b44c5d7a2","tid":1521752,"uid":103325,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"校長好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過做擔保要香港人要做得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:45:53.000Z","msg":"唔知教育部駐香港代表出唔出到面"},{"pid":"ef8c711b15f891e55d75a16f321c78e142590585","tid":1521752,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"73b7cc832b48c13fc588410d820bb6752cf7a204","tid":1521752,"uid":53672,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我係民國人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fdf45f5989e24ec1f78431380d896e8a97d384","tid":1521752,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"台灣校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfde6685388250e3be3a48c4f20b5e97d35e465","tid":1521752,"uid":278391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"人家的校長"},{"pid":"6fb02ccd3788ccbdd56d637921fe0cf679844c06","tid":1521752,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"可能拒絕入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74ee524e7395c45f46d81a1047a3b282eb8e255","tid":1521752,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c70893aab0f6b95261ce5ca8edf6e02c4d5b5eb","tid":1521752,"uid":3241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"屌， 錢大康果堆垃圾廢賤人渣學棍"},{"pid":"f91f95805c5709087a8598cf25a26b4829889a44","tid":1521752,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"就杜浩成法官作出有罪假定及煽動他人侵權之言論作出投訴（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1521682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1521682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d71f38c8ab1ffe5d600078a2d9f0dda5cb29db05","tid":1521752,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ad965842c788af769b183856dfd7789864f327d","tid":1521752,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb5b1bc374e6b8066b27fc153f3db1ae1cdf644","tid":1521752,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"Do you feel ashamed? The principals of Hong Kong universities."},{"pid":"3fb3d195776ad687866c502b90c156259ab5d854","tid":1521752,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"蔡元培嗰種文人風骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9581ac5299e735dcfca8823e35d3efd18f760d8","tid":1521752,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467d0cb23fa92f7d0cfadcb11916a191f88d5fdd","tid":1521752,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"國立東華大學校長趙涵㨗任期將於2020年1月屆滿，校方年初舉行校長續任同意權行使投票，包括教職人員、學生組成的96名校務會議代表，共有91人投票，同意續任票數80票，以近9成同意票數順利續任。<br />\n<br />\n趙涵㨗1993年曾任東華大學電機系系主任、電子計算機中心主任等職務長達13年，2010年接任國立宜蘭大學第三任校長，直到3年前再次回鍋東華，擔任第七任校長，如今也將續任第八任校長。<br />\n<br />\n此外，趙涵㨗出身電機工程與資訊科學背景，長期推動東部地區數位教育，致力推動智慧校園，在學術研究、產學合作、技術轉移、國際化方面皆有著墨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據「泰晤士報高等教育專刊」公布世界大學排名，東華大學去年首度入榜，今年最新2019世界大學排名中，更在台灣入榜的大學中躍進了7名，名列台灣第14名，其中國際化程度項目排名第6名，研究聲望項目排名第10名，論文影響力項目排名第12名，各個項目都有明顯成長。<br />\n<br />\n東華大學昨校長續任同意權行使投票，由85名一級主管、老師、職員及11名學生組成的校務會議代表，昨天出席人數共91人，投票率高達94％，以同意續任票數近9成順利續任。趙涵㨗說，獲得師生的託付，責任更為重大了，一定會鞠躬盡瘁時時不已。"},{"pid":"b6d3623446542017083ed61f03299c3fcf111c7b","tid":1521752,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"有當年北大蔡校長風範，反觀香港各大既所謂「校長」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42ed0428b1bc4a9cf2bfb28427d3d89cd40dae6","tid":1521752,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"呢d先係真正既校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9bd3edeaf1e3099aaee8b4c487030739b00706","tid":1521752,"uid":136971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a9dc1625322a1924b8148d10c84a5b32f29b60","tid":1521752,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"香港各大學校長都係垃圾 <br />\n學生都保護唔到 做校長？<br />\n一個的士司機都有風骨過你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e88de35a20fb49b488620094adc56424306f08","tid":1521752,"uid":284100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"香港有咁好既校長就好<br />\n可惜無啦<br />\n成班都係奶共垃圾"}]}